ing approach will help to build predictive models for diagnosis and prognosis of the disease. Essentially, the work that is being suggested represents the coming together of state-of-the-art computational techniques with the demands of contemporary health care, signaling the beginning of a revolutionary period in biosignal analysis and its social ramifications. The suggested framework aims to usher in a new era of individualized, data-driven healthcare delivery by empowering individuals, professionals, and healthcare systems alike through its revolutionary methodology.}
